Class UserManager

java.lang.Object
com.group6.users.UserManager
public class UserManager extends Object
Manages user authentication and retrieval.

This class is responsible for loading, storing, and managing users. It interacts with UserStorage to retrieve and validate users.

    • isValidLogin

      public boolean isValidLogin(String nric, String password)
      Validates if the given NRIC and password match a registered user.

      This method checks if the provided credentials match an existing user stored in the system.

      Parameters:
      nric - The NRIC entered by the user.
      password - The password entered by the user.
      Returns:
      true if the credentials are valid, false otherwise.
